♪I hear my heartbeat roaring in sorrow♪

189
00:12:25,837 --> 00:12:27,649
♪I was abandoned♪

190
00:12:27,650 --> 00:12:30,686
♪Dreaming of you in the same place♪

191
00:12:30,687 --> 00:12:35,399
♪Cold eyes♪

192
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:39,999
♪Searching for
traces of light in the dark♪

193
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:45,049
♪Learning to fade from the crowd♪

194
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:47,774
♪The endless dark clouds♪

195
00:12:47,775 --> 00:12:49,524
♪I miss you so much♪

196
00:12:49,525 --> 00:12:53,186
♪Longing for an echo of salvation♪

197
00:12:53,187 --> 00:12:55,319
♪Yet no one responds♪

198
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,440
Ouch.

199
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,049
Stop moving.

200
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,080
Or I'll let you be a cripple.

201
00:13:03,950 --> 00:13:05,959
♪Yet I still can't find a trace of you♪

202
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,919
You...

203
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:08,160
Be gentle.

204
00:13:09,037 --> 00:13:12,911
♪Like a whale drowning in the cracks
of the deep sea♪

205
00:13:12,912 --> 00:13:18,636
♪Thinking of you,
I lose myself completely♪

206
00:13:18,637 --> 00:13:22,439
♪My heart shattered,
withered into pieces♪

207
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,960
Now you know the pain.

208
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,240
Where's the spirit from
when you broke the table?

209
00:13:28,225 --> 00:13:32,149
♪Screaming as I fall
into the darkest abyss♪

210
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:36,424
♪Echoing back is only the tide
of loneliness♪

211
